== History ==
History of bookmarks (favorites) sync:
* 2005 - [[Maxthon]] 1.3
* 2006 - [[Google Browser Sync]] (extension for Firefox)
* 2007 - [[Opera (web browser)|Opera]]
* 2007 - [[Firefox]]
* 2009 - [[Google Chrome]]
* 2012 - Eversync (extension for Firefox)

